food.name: Hot Dog on a WG Bun
food.description: These hot dogs are a fun, healthy twist on the traditional ballpark dog. We take plump, juicy beef hot dog and cover it in a whole grain wheat bun. Combined with all the fixins, it looks like a regular hot dog, but tastes better and is much healthier. students love them!

food.name: Sweet Potato Fries
food.description: A healthier (and tastier!) alternative to traditional French fries, these premium sweet potato slim sticks pack a mountain of nutrition and flavor into every bite.

food.name: Cinnamon Pancakes
food.description: Our fluffy pancakes are glazed with cinnamon, perfecting our take on this American classic. students love them!

food.name: Grilled Cheese Sandwich
food.description: An American classic, the grilled cheese sandwich is hard to beat. Our chefs did their best to be true to this student favorite, and put a healthy twist on things. Reduced-fat cheddar cheese and whole wheat bread make all the healthy difference, and offer a rich, crunchy taste that will have your students asking for seconds.

food.name: Potato Smiles
food.description: Potato smiles are fries BAKED in a smiley, circular face. These delightful fries are low in sodium & cholesterol, putting smiles on faces of students each time we serve them.

food.name: Cheese Filled Bread Sticks
food.description: Everyone loves hot bread-sticks just out of the oven - especially when they’re filled with cheese!

food.name: Marinara Sauce Dip Cup
food.description: Vine ripened tomatoes simmered with Italian spices combine to make the perfect topping for many dishes and a fun dipping sauce.
